EDIT: I'm surprised everyone assumed I did this (think...), well to be honest that was the wrong link. I've fixed it now, but PLEASE POST & give ideas that you would like to share :(.
Design [url=http://smashbros.deviantart.com/art/Portfolio-Design-42927261]inspired by [i]SmashBros[/i][/url] of DeviantArt.com. Made november 21, 2008 for practice by Jarod -- aka Server-Unknown.net at 7:03 AM in the morning, finishing at 5:29 PM (-5 GMT). The design is called "Weeeeeesh!".
Preview of the design can be found by clicking [url=http://jarod.b.angelfire.com//layouts/Designs/Weeeeeesh/Weeeeeesh.png]here[/url]. If you have any questions, please ask. If you have any tips, please tell me! I'm a new comer to web design's and want to expand my web designing ability.
If you want to modify(or download) it you can click [url=http://jarod.b.angelfire.com/layouts/Designs/Weeeeeesh/Weeeeeesh.xcf]here[/url] to download it.
